      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那Loading之后应该有两个分支吧？一个是正常拿到数据，另一个是请求失败的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
