      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Success和Error两个终态。Success之后可以Reset回到Idle，Error的话可以Retry回到Idle，也可以直接Abort退回到Education_LMS_Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
